#. ClusterTraitGenerationManager.STRINGS.UI.CGM_MAINSCREENEXPORT.DETAILS.FOOTER.BUTTONS.GENERATECLUSTERBUTTON.TOOLTIP_CLUSTERPLACEMENTFAILED_COMETS
